</emphasis>
Erzurum Province (Özkan &amp; Soysal 
<number box="[867,930,1560,1586]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" value="1989.0">1989</number>
); Kayseri Province (
<bibRefCitation author="Ozkan" box="[1168,1383,1560,1586]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" refString="Ozkan, M., Erman, O. &amp; Boyaci, Y. O. (1996) Sultan Sazligi'nin (Kayseri) Su Akari (Hydrachnellae, Acari) Faunasi Uzerine Bir Arastirma. Turkish Journal of Zoology, 20, 95 - 98." type="journal article" year="1996">
